OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781107889
OL,3,CReform UK council leader pulls support
OL,4,Cfor Pride in St Helens
OL,6,FA Reform UK council leader has
OL,7,Fannounced the council will no longer
OL,8,Fsupport LGBTQ+ Pride, claiming he has
OL,9,F"instructed officers to cease
OL,10,Fengagement with all aspects of the
OL,11,Fevent."
OL,13,FDr George Woodward - Reform UK Leader
OL,14,Fof St Helens Borough Council - shared
OL,15,Fa statement on Facebook claiming the
OL,16,Fcouncil "won't be supporting or
OL,17,Fpromoting Pride."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
