FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781107889
OL,3,CReform UK council leader pulls support
OL,4,Cfor Pride in St Helens
OL,6,FThe statement said: "We don't consider
OL,7,Fcelebrations of sexuality, especially
OL,8,Fthose with left-wing political
OL,9,Fleanings such as Pride, to be
OL,10,Fappropriate for St Helens Borough
OL,11,FCouncil to dedicate valuable officer
OL,12,Fresources.
OL,14,FI am also deeply concerned that Pride
OL,15,Fhas become affiliated with harmful
OL,16,Ftransgender ideology. As a council, we
OL,17,Fhave a duty of care towards young
OL,18,Fchildren in the borough.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781107889
OL,3,CReform UK council leader pulls support
OL,4,Cfor Pride in St Helens
OL,6,F"Being affiliated with a movement that
OL,7,Foften results in lifelong medical harm
OL,8,Fin young impressionable children is
OL,9,Fnot the direction in which I want St
OL,10,FHelens Council to travel."
OL,12,FCouncillor Woodward - who became
OL,13,Fleader after Reform UK won a majority
OL,14,Fin the May 2026 local elections -
OL,15,Fconfirmed that "individuals, the
OL,16,Fprivate sector, and charities" are
OL,17,Fwelcome to continue supporting the
OL,18,Fevent.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
