PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781107889
OL,3,CReform UK council leader pulls support
OL,4,Cfor Pride in St Helens
OL,6,FDespite the statement posted on
OL,7,FTuesday 9 June 2026, St Helens Pride
OL,8,Fwent ahead at The World of Glass on
OL,9,FSaturday 6 June.
OL,11,FThe event included community stalls,
OL,12,Ffamily-friendly activities and live
OL,13,Fmusic - funded by local communities.
OL,15,FLiverpool City Region's (LCR) LGBTQ+
OL,16,Fcharity condemned the announcement,
OL,17,Fstating they are "unfortunately not
OL,18,Fsurprised".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781107889
OL,3,CReform UK council leader pulls support
OL,4,Cfor Pride in St Helens
OL,6,FA statement from LCR Pride said: "The
OL,7,FLCR Pride Foundation is deeply
OL,8,Fdisappointed, though unfortunately not
OL,9,Fsurprised, by the divisive and
OL,10,Fexclusionary statement issued by the
OL,11,FLeader of St Helens Borough Council.
OL,13,F"Pride is not a partisan or 'left-
OL,14,Fwing' political movement; it is a
OL,15,Ffundamental stand for human rights,
OL,16,Fdignity, and equality.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781107889
OL,3,CReform UK council leader pulls support
OL,4,Cfor Pride in St Helens
OL,6,F"For a local authority leader to frame
OL,7,Fthe celebration of marginalised
OL,8,Fcommunities as an inappropriate use of
OL,9,Fresources shows a fundamental
OL,10,Fmisunderstanding of the Public Sector
OL,11,FEquality Duty, which legally requires
OL,12,Fcouncils to foster good relations and
OL,13,Feliminate discrimination.
OL,15,F"Furthermore, we categorically condemn
OL,16,Fthe Leader's use of transphobic dog-
OL,17,Fwhistles. To weaponise the concept of
OL,18,Fa 'duty of care' to justify the
OL,19,Fmarginalisation of transgender people
OL,20,Fis a failure of leadership.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781107889
OL,3,CReform UK council leader pulls support
OL,4,Cfor Pride in St Helens
OL,6,F"It causes direct, tangible harm to
OL,7,Fthe very young people the Council
OL,8,Fclaims it wants to protect. Trans
OL,9,Fidentities are not a 'harmful
OL,10,Fideology'; they are a reality for many
OL,11,Fresidents within St Helens who deserve
OL,12,Fa council that supports them, rather
OL,13,Fthan one that actively targets them
OL,14,Ffor political point-scoring.
OL,16,F"To the LGBT+ community in St Helens:
OL,17,Fwe see you, we stand with you, and we
OL,18,Fwill not let this type of rhetoric go
OL,19,Funchallenged. Pride will continue to
OL,20,Fthrive in St Helens, with or without
OL,21,Fthe Council Leader's endorsement."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781107889
OL,3,CReform UK council leader pulls support
OL,4,Cfor Pride in St Helens
OL,6,FSt Helens Borough Council also
OL,7,Fannounced it would cease its support
OL,8,Ffor planned Refugee Week events in
OL,9,FJune 2026. Councillor Woodward said
OL,10,Fthis was a move to "put British people
OL,11,Ffirst."
OL,13,FResponding to the announcement, Labour
OL,14,FMP for St Helens North David Baines
OL,15,Fclaimed in a statement that the Reform
OL,16,FUK council has told council libraries
OL,17,Fto "remove any references to Pride,
OL,18,Fand to rebrand any events which had
OL,19,Fbeen planned."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781107889
OL,3,CReform UK council leader pulls support
OL,4,Cfor Pride in St Helens
OL,6,FHe said: "Reform won the election so
OL,7,Fthey have every right to make
OL,8,Fdecisions like this. Myself and others
OL,9,Fknew that this was the sort of
OL,10,Fdivisive, shortsighted and dangerous
OL,11,Fthing they would do and that's part of
OL,12,Fthe reason we fought to keep them out
OL,13,Fin May.
OL,15,F"We lost the argument - but that
OL,16,Fdoesn't mean the fight to promote
OL,17,Fdecent and inclusive British values is
OL,18,Fover.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781107889
OL,3,CReform UK council leader pulls support
OL,4,Cfor Pride in St Helens
OL,6,F"First they came for Refugee Week,
OL,7,Fspreading misinformation about the
OL,8,Fcost and alleged savings, and mixing
OL,9,Fup refugees and illegal immigrants.
OL,10,FNow they've come for our LGBT friends,
OL,11,Ffamily and neighbours who still suffer
OL,12,Fdiscrimination, even though the Pride
OL,13,Fevents cost the council nothing.
OL,15,F"Elected politicians are community
OL,16,Fleaders. Their words matter. Their
OL,17,Factions matter even more."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781107889
OL,3,CReform UK council leader pulls support
OL,4,Cfor Pride in St Helens
OL,6,FMr Baines went on to urge councillors
OL,7,F"to focus on bringing people together
OL,8,Fand on other things that really
OL,9,Fmatter", instead of "spending their
OL,10,Ftime stoking culture wars and trying
OL,11,Fto divide us."
OL,13,FJames Dunn - independent councillor
OL,14,Ffor Rainhill - shared a comment
OL,15,Fdisagreeing with Councillor Woodward.
OL,16,FHe said: "It is important that
OL,17,Fresidents know this view is not shared
OL,18,Fby everyone in the council chamber."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781107889
OL,3,CReform UK council leader pulls support
OL,4,Cfor Pride in St Helens
OL,6,FHe added: "People can absolutely
OL,7,Fdebate council funding, officer
OL,8,Fresources and what role the local
OL,9,Fauthority should play in events with
OL,10,Fcosts attached, particularly when you
OL,11,Fran on a promise to cut costs but
OL,12,FIndividuals, charities, community
OL,13,Fgroups and the private sector do not
OL,14,Fneed permission from the council to
OL,15,Fsupport Pride.
OL,17,F"They already did support it on
OL,18,FSaturday, and it looks like we both
OL,19,Fmissed a great day. I won't next year.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
